.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, marigold, iris, amaryllis
5 different games are played: go, domino, bridge, mah-jongg, whist
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, pop, r&b, funk, disco
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tulipmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, peach, pear, pomegranate, cauliflower
1. the person playing go is the person who growsmarigold
2. the person playing swedish is the person eating pear
3. the person playing domino is the fan of funk
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsiris
5. the person who growssunflower is the fan of pop
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating peach
7. the person who growsamaryllis is the dunhill-smoker
8. the fan of r&b is in the middle
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage
11. the person eating cauliflowers is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the tulipmaster-smoker is the fan of punk
13. the person playing bridge is the prince-smoker
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who growstulip
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of disco

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Flower		|    amaryllis	|     tulip	|      marigold	|     sunflower	|     iris	|
| Game	|   mah-jongg	|    domino	|    go	|    bridge	|    swedish	|
| Food		|     cabbage	|    cauliflower	|     peach	|     pomegranate	|      pear	|
| Music-Genre	|    disco	|     funk	|     r&b	|    pop	|      punk	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   tulipmaster	|
